text: Her is gemearcod hu manega hyda landes þureð eorl betæht hafað into sancte Cuðberhtes stowe.
Nu is æryst on Smiþatune twa hyda landes and on Creic twa hyda and on Suþtune anre hyde þæt he afað ðam halegan were to lofe and to weorðmynde gegyfen a to<../images/etail.gif>cean life.
And se þe þyses ofteo hæbbe hit wiþ God gemæne and wið ðone halgan wer ær oððe siþor.
